Title: MCP Kitchen Scale Electronic Digital LCD Screen 7 kg Weighing Scale(White)
Description: So you are hosting a small dinner at home and have downloaded a recipe from the Internet. Apart from the basic ingredients, one instrument that you will definitely need is a measuring scale. This kitchen weighing scale from MCP is an ideal solution to all your concerns about weighing ingredients accurately, so you can serve a flavorful dish to your guests. Digital Scale A large display window exhibits the resultant weight in clear digital numerals. No need to convert the units of measurement for various ingredients, as you can choose the unit of measurement from g, kg, oz, and lb as per your recipe. Design Features This battery-operated machine is crafted from plastic and is designed to weigh ingredients up to a capacity of 7 kgs. You can easily replace the used batteries with fresh and fully charged ones when they drain out. Tare function The tare function lets you reset the scale to zero after placing an empty container, so the resultant weight displayed is only that of the ingredient that you actually want to weigh.

Jojoba Oil Reduces Annoyed Skin And Improves The Natural Development Of Collagen. It Also Offers Efficient Protection Towards Sun. Jojoba Oil Can Also Be Used As A Moisturizer Before Make Up Or As A Make Up Remover Or As A Hair Serum As Well.
